items.description: The Southern entrance into Hilton McLean Tysons Corner hotel.

Mrs. Jo's Petite Eats was founded by Chef Erinn Roth and is a great patisserie and cafe that is Woman and Veteran owned located in McLean, Virginia.

This was an attendee favorite last year and we're pleased to announce that they will be open for brunch over the entire weekend.

Address: 7940 Jones Branch Dr, Tysons, VA 22102
Phone: 571.327.9431
